<taxonomicName authorityName="Boisduval" authorityYear="1828" box="[930,1014,1435,1457]" class="Insecta" family="Sesiidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="596" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Sesiidae</taxonomicName>
picture ffi 0167–2018. Alar expanse 20.7 mm; 2) ditto, ventral view. 
